in_home&value=hot01\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/654b7fa1952f8b50_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/001Na93Ily1gjqwwdzt0wj60j709mmyr02.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/654b7fa1952f8b50_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#夏之光恋情#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#夏之光恋情# 近日，有媒体拍到R1SE成员夏之光与一神秘女子到驾校练车，疑似恋情曝光。当天，两人十指紧扣走出家门，女生说话时夏之光细心帮她把头发别到耳后 。回家时，一辆车从女生身边开过，夏之光更是一把把她拉回来并搂入怀中，动作亲密。新浪娱乐就此求证夏之光工作人员，对方暂未回应。 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/05a057d250ffaf0a_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot02\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/05a057d250ffaf0a_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/0033ImPzly1gjqgii2qpfj60u00zck4a02.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/05a057d250ffaf0a_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#江苏大学通报学生坠楼身亡事件#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【#江苏大学通报学生坠楼身亡事件#】15日@江苏大学 通报，10月12日17时03分左右，该校食品与生物工程学院一学生从主A楼6楼卫生间坠楼。后经抢救确认，该学生已无生命体征。警方调查结论为“高空坠楼，排除他杀”。通报称，学校对该同学的不幸离世深感惋惜并哀悼，并将全力配合警方调查、协助家长善后。 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/ad58702bf96455a8_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot03\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/ad58702bf96455a8_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/h5.sinaimg.cn\/upload\/100\/721\/2019\/03\/14\/vote.png\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/ad58702bf96455a8_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#任豪道歉#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#任豪道歉# @R1SE-任豪 #任豪回应# 任豪发微博回应，并且和R1SE的队友道歉，决定暂停在社交媒体上除工作外的个人发言，作为对自己的告诫[doge][doge][doge]这算是默认了吗？ http:\/\/t.cn\/A6bp9PNC ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/3432f0478b0e4ba6_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot04\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/3432f0478b0e4ba6_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/wx1.sinaimg.cn\/orj480\/744bc6a6ly1gjqhi0jg1uj21hc0u0grx.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/3432f0478b0e4ba6_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">张培萌妻子称只想要女儿抚养权<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【#张培萌妻子称只想要女儿抚养权# 男方：无中生有 她强势还给我洗脑】10月15日，短跑名将张培萌妻子发长文控诉其遭张培萌家暴，并晒出遭家暴的受伤照。15日晚，张培萌妻子表示，曝光此事只为夺回孩子抚养权。随后，#张培萌方回应#称，家暴属无中生有，其妻子性格强势，一直索要最好生活和钱。 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/a9a48963a6b34a12_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot05\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/a9a48963a6b34a12_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/wx2.sinaimg.cn\/orj480\/0067MtiAly1gjqvqd8ok9j31hc0u0kd9.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/a9a48963a6b34a12_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#李栋旭身材#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#李栋旭身材# 《九尾狐传》李栋旭饰演的李砚因为救了智雅，被罚绑在雪山山洞中七年（约等于现实的一周），不能吃、不能睡也不能死去。李砚半裸跪在地上，露出完美的胸肌腹肌，再加上痛苦的表情和绝望的嘶吼。太绝了！这是阿乐配看的画面吗[色]http:\/\/t.cn\/A6bpDYcp ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n    <div class=\"UG_box_foot\">\n        <a href=\"\/\/weibo.com\/a\/hot\/realtime\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">查看更多<i class=\"W_ficon ficon_arrow_right S_ficon\">a<\/i><\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n"})</script>
